cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.LG, cs.CR

This paper focuses on the intersection of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), specifically in the context of decision making. It also touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as the need for explainability and interpretability in AI (cs.CR).
